er Schmeichel \u2013 Century of International Appearances\"]. ''RSSSF''. Retrieved 14 July 2012.</ref>\n|}\n\n===International goals===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!# \n!Date \n!Venue\n!Opponent\n!Score\n!Result\n!Competition\n|-\n| 1 || 3 June 2000 || [[Parken Stadium]], [[Copenhagen]], Denmark || {{fb|BEL}} ||align=\"center\"| '''2'''\u20131 ||align=\"center\"| 2\u20132 || [[Exhibition game|Friendly]]\n|}\n\n==Honours==\nSource:<ref name=\"Honours\">{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/players-coaches/people=57693/profile.html |title=The great Dane with the big bark |publisher=FIFA |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170528082710/http://www.fifa.com/fifa-tournaments/players-coaches/people=57693/profile.html |archivedate=28 May 2017}}</ref>\n\n===Club===\n'''Br\u00f8ndby''' \n* [[Danish 1st Division]]/[[Danish Superliga]]: [[1987 Danish 1st Division|1987]], [[1988 Danish 1st Division|1988]], [[1990 Danish 1st Division|1990]], [[1991 Danish Superliga|1991]]\n* [[Danish Cup]]: [[1989 Danish Cup|1989]]\n\n'''Manchester United''' \n* [[Premier League]]: [[1992\u201393 FA Premier League|1992\u201393]], [[1993\u201394 FA Premier League|1993\u201394]], [[1995\u201396 FA Premier League|1995\u201396]], [[1996\u201397 FA Premier League|1996\u201397]], [[1998\u201399 FA Premier League|1998\u201399]]<ref name=PL>{{cite web |url=https://www.premierleague.com/players/307/Peter-Schmeichel/overview |title=Peter Schmeichel: Overview |publisher=Premier League |accessdate=18 April 2018}}</ref>\n* [[FA Cup]]: [[1993\u201394 FA Cup|1993\u201394]], [[1995\u201396 FA Cup|1995\u201396]], [[1998\u201399 FA Cup|1998\u201399]]\n* [[Football League Cup]] : [[1991\u201392 Football League Cup|1991\u201392]]\n* [[FA Charity Shield]]: [[1993 FA Charity Shield|1993]], [[1994 FA Charity Shield|1994]], [[1996 FA Charity Shield|1996]], [[1997 FA Charity Shield|1997]]\n* [[UEFA Champions League]]: [[1998\u201399 UEFA Champions League|1998\u201399]]\n* [[European Super Cup]]: [[1